vg></div></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oma1720015839839.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oma1720015839839.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oma1720015839839.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ojk1665702596093\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__display_215968\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Presents the form on the screen as display-only.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__topic_d71138e1_d71139e1_d71140e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__p_d71141e1_d71142e1_d71143e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span>{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/menu</span>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">LitFieldName</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__section_w2724ab1b7b5_w2725ab1b7_w2726ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__p_d71144e1_d71145e1_d71146e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">display CLIENT_DETAIL</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__topic_d46747e1_d46748e1_d46749e1_d46750e1_d46751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d596279e80\">\n                       \n Qualifiers\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6395e1_d6396e1_d6397e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6395e1_d6396e1_d6397e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6395e1_d6396e1_d6397e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6395e1_d6396e1_d6397e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/menu</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6395e1_d6396e1_d6397e1__entry__2\">\n Activates the menu trigger at field, entity, form, or application level (the one at the lowest level that contains ProcScript) when the form appears.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__topic_d46752e1_d46753e1_d46754e1_d46755e1_d46756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d596279e126\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LitFieldName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1__entry__2\">\n Literal\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6398e1_d6399e1_d6400e1__entry__3\">\n Literal name of the field in which to position the cursor; do not enclose the name in double quotation marks (\"). The cursor is positioned in the field named.\n <p class=\"p\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">LitFieldName</var> is omitted or is not painted on the form, the cursor is positioned on the first painted field (that is, in the field nearest the top left corner of the form).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__topic_d46757e1_d46758e1_d46759e1_d46760e1_d46761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d596279e187\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">10</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__2\">\n The user used ^QUIT to leave the form that was started with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">9</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__2\">\n The user used ^ACCEPT to leave the form that was started with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__2\">\n Success.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6401e1_d6402e1_d6403e1__entry__2\">\n The application is running in batch mode. Use a test on <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$batch</span> to avoid this.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$display</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__1\">\n -33\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_BATCH_ONLY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__3\">\n Statement not allowed in batch mode. Use a test on <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$batch</span> to avoid this.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__1\">\n -1401\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_PROMPT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__3\">\n Prompted field not valid.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__1\">\n -1402\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_STATEMENT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ojk1665702596093__table_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1__entry__3\">\n Statement not allowed in this trigger. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span> statement is not in an exec operation.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__topic_d46762e1_d46763e1_d46764e1_d46765e1_d46766e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d596279e392\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__p_d71159e1_d71160e1_d71161e1\">Use in Form components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__p_d71162e1_d71163e1_d71164e1\">Allowed only in the exec operation.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__topic_d46767e1_d46768e1_d46769e1_d46770e1_d46771e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d596279e404\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__p_d71168e1_d71169e1_d71170e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span> statement presents the current form as display-only. Data in the form cannot be modified. (You can also use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> with the instance property <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISPLAY=TRUE</code> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">run/display</span> to start a form in display-only mode.)</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__section_w4w_n1c_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d596279e425\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ojk1665702596093__pre_as3_41c_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n CUST_NBR = $1\n retrieve\n message \"%%$hits customers match search profile\"\n display CUSTNAME\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwk1665702595783.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>edit</a><p>Display the component in preparation for user input.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dic1665702596168.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$batch</a><p>Return the batch mode indicator.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7433507\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7433507\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "display Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Version: Use up/down arrow keys to navigate, Esc to collapse. Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Last Updated Juli 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Presents the form on the screen as display-only. display { /menu } { LitFieldName } Example: display CLIENT_DETAIL Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /menu Activates the menu trigger at field, entity, form, or application level (the one at the lowest level that contains ProcScript) when the form appears. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description LitFieldName Literal Literal name of the field in which to position the cursor; do not enclose the name in double quotation marks (\"). The cursor is positioned in the field named. If LitFieldName is omitted or is not painted on the form, the cursor is positioned on the first painted field (that is, in the field nearest the top left corner of the form). Return Values Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 10 The user used ^QUIT to leave the form that was started with display . 9 The user used ^ACCEPT to leave the form that was started with display . 0 Success. -16 The application is running in batch mode. Use a test on $batch to avoid this. Table 4. Values commonly returned by $procerror following $display Value Error constant Meaning -33 <UGENERR_BATCH_ONLY> Statement not allowed in batch mode. Use a test on $batch to avoid this. -1401 <UPROCERR_PROMPT> Prompted field not valid. -1402 <UPROCERR_STATEMENT> Statement not allowed in this trigger. The display statement is not in an exec operation. Use Use in Form components. Allowed only in the exec operation. Description The display statement presents the current form as display-only. Data in the form cannot be modified. (You can also use newinstance with the instance property DISPLAY=TRUE or run/display to start a form in display-only mode.) Example: Using display operation exec CUST_NBR = $1 retrieve message \"%%$hits customers match search profile\" display CUSTNAME end; exec Copy Related Links edit Display the component in preparation for user input. $batch Return the batch mode indicator. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}